        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_PRO/Scenes/Missions/Paris/_scene_paris.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository bbd56dbf-f855-4389-88b3-f8e8a924cc8b).Image",
        "Description": "The client has intel that Japser Won Sheung Chit, the infamous drug trafficker, is involved in the upcoming fashion show in Paris. While not being present directly, he has sent various informants to gather information in his stead. The client wants these 5 eliminated. You do not have much time to complete this taks as they will be leaving the show in approximately 12 minutes. Good luck, 47.",
